__compat.description: IANA time zone names in `timeZone` option

deno.notes: Only the locale data for `en-US` is available.

nodejs.notes: Before version 13.0.0, only the locale data for `en-US` is available by default. When other locales are specified, the function silently falls back to `en-US`. To make full ICU (locale) data available before version 13, see [Node.js documentation on the `--with-intl` option](https://nodejs.org/docs/latest/api/intl.html#intl_options_for_building_node_js) and how to provide the data.
